5:["$","$L10",null,{"project":{"_id":"fb4a21d0-12b8-4b6d-b6bd-d5953a4d8baa","body":{"conclusion":"Addressing Karachi's energy deficit requires a dual strategy: rehabilitating existing thermal capacity and accelerating investment in distributed renewable generation. The report provides a ranked priority matrix for infrastructure intervention.","methodology":"Data was sourced from NEPRA annual reports, K-Electric published data, and academic literature. Load curve analysis was performed for residential, commercial, and industrial sectors. Power plant efficiency ratings were compared against design specifications.","overview":"This technical report examines Karachi's electric power infrastructure, covering installed generation capacity, transmission constraints, and the structural mismatch between peak demand and available supply. The study was conducted to understand systemic vulnerabilities and identify pathways for grid modernization.","results":"Karachi's peak demand regularly exceeds reliable generation capacity by 15–20% during summer months. Transmission losses average 18%, significantly above the international benchmark of 8–10%. Aging thermal plants operate at 55–65% efficiency against design efficiencies of 75–80%."},"category":"Energy & Power","description":"Extensive research on Karachi's energy infrastructure, analyzing power plant operations and energy demand/supply dynamics.","featured":true,"id":"fb4a21d0-12b8-4b6d-b6bd-d5953a4d8baa","images":[{"alt":"Karachi power grid map","asset":{"_ref":"image-c4a707fcd3df88b205a516ae26c227cfbc826bb6-6000x4000-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/c4a707fcd3df88b205a516ae26c227cfbc826bb6-6000x4000.jpg"},{"alt":"Demand-supply analysis chart","asset":{"_ref":"image-d4a1c3843c3ab947a2fce919c2f975b36328a96f-4000x2649-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/d4a1c3843c3ab947a2fce919c2f975b36328a96f-4000x2649.jpg"},{"alt":"Power plant facility","asset":{"_ref":"image-4e9c7fc2ba9b466c097d0cf864ebf602008f4c32-4608x3072-jpg","_type":"reference"},"src":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/c2t45jcn/production/4e9c7fc2ba9b466c097d0cf864ebf602008f4c32-4608x3072.jpg"}],"slug":"pakistan-energy-infrastructure-report","title":"Pakistan Energy Infrastructure Report","year":"2023"}}]
